Example
The user-agent header sent by your browser is:

Copy
let x = "User-agent header sent: " + navigator.userAgent;

Description
The userAgent property returns the value of the user-agent header sent by the browser to the server.

The returned value contains information about the name, version and platform of the browser.

This property is read-only.

Browser Compatibility
Chrome.png	Node.png	Firefox.png	Safari.png	Edge.png	Opera.png
userAgent	Yes	Yes	Yes	Yes	Yes	Yes
Syntax
Copy
let a = navigator.userAgent;
Return Value
A String, representing the user agent string for the current browser
